TopicTitle: STAND By for liftoff of KSP 1.1 Career Mode LP

Articles.Content:
Sup Kerbanauts!

How's everybody's missions going? 

I thought just before i release my first video of my career mode Let's Play for the 1.1 release of KSP, i would highlight some of the cool missions ive completed so far in the 1.0.5 version. Hopefully some of you will find the videos interesting enough to subscribe to my youtube channel, but if not, it would be fun to get know u guys anyway and share tips and strategies. Below i'll link a few of the more interesting and fun contracts and missions ive completed, and fingers crossed some of u will join me on my adventures in the Kerbisphere!

Manned Duna landing - https://youtu.be/Jnk6BrThuUw: 

Mining Rig on Gilly - https://youtu.be/OZis4bwAMeY

Building a Mun Base with Rovers - https://youtu.be/zgqt49iblvg

Hope to see some of you over at my channel!

Take care out there, space is infinite...

R.Einstein
